embed.title: Hey there!
embed.description: Nice to see you here! You can support us by subscribing on youtube -> [YouTube](https://www.youtube.com/fireupdate) <- and also join our  [Discord](https://discord.gg/3FAd4Yu)!

fields.name: Main motive of the channel?
fields.value: This channel is all about gaming. We do live streams every single day to entertain people out there. 80% of the revenue earned from the channel goes to #FireForIndia.

fields.name: What is #FireForIndia?
fields.value: #FireForIndia is basically a hashtag which is used by us to support India. This means, We contribute 80% of the money to charity and the whole process is defined as #FireForIndia.

fields.name: Discord
fields.value: Make sure to join our [Discord](https://discord.gg/3FAd4Yu) to support the movement!

embed.description: A Discord server where you will find lots of custom bots developed by people around the globe, You can try them out for the first time and enjoy!
